00:01:09.740 --> 00:01:12.170
And all those objects
are oscillating

00:01:12.170 --> 00:01:14.510
in just one direction--
for example,

00:01:14.510 --> 00:01:16.580
up and down in one direction.

00:01:16.580 --> 00:01:22.460
That's actually one measure
