01:01:07.600 --> 01:01:13.030
And it got accepted and
then recorded by the scope.

01:01:13.030 --> 01:01:15.240
Now I have all of those--

01:01:15.240 --> 01:01:17.160
OK, all are not so
perfect, but those

01:01:17.160 --> 01:01:23.320
are metals which have
many, many strips

01:01:23.320 --> 01:01:26.480
or many, many little rods here.

01:01:26.480 --> 01:01:32.210
And my initial
