01:03:00.140 --> 01:03:01.590
Can you see it?

01:03:01.590 --> 01:03:02.730
Nothing happened, right?

01:03:02.730 --> 01:03:05.460
Because those electrons--
oh my god, crisis coming,

01:03:05.460 --> 01:03:08.500
but now there's nothing I can
