01:10:26.010 --> 01:10:29.520
polarized in y,
then I am in trouble

01:10:29.520 --> 01:10:33.010
because I don't know
how to calculate

01:10:33.010 --> 01:10:36.290
what is this intensity.

01:10:36.290 --> 01:10:44.490
So basically maybe all of them
pass through or all of them

01:10:44.490 --> 01:10:47.430
doesn't pass through.

01:10:47.430 --> 01:10:50.670
Then we can do this experiment.

01:10:50.670 --> 01:10:52.810
And this is the result--

01:10:52.810 --> 01:10:55.590
