because that

01:11:25.840 --> 01:11:29.970
means a single photon is not
like a single object, which

01:11:29.970 --> 01:11:33.480
is actually passing through
all those polarizers.

01:11:33.480 --> 01:11:42.630
But they actually
act also like waves.

